Name: TracWikiTemplates
Version: 0.3.0rc2
Summary: Trac Plugin to pre-format parts of the Wiki page using it
Home-page: http://wikitmplates.ufsoft.org
Author: Pedro Algarvio
Author-email: ufs@ufsoft.org
